            <h2 class="text-center">Pooja</h2>
            <p class="text-justify">
                Pooja, a sacred ritual in Hinduism and other Indian traditions, involves a series of worship practices aimed at honoring and connecting with deities and divine forces. This spiritual practice, which translates to "worship" or "reverence," is an integral part of daily life for many people and holds profound significance in the spiritual and cultural landscape.
            </p>
